text: Manfred Queck (10 August 1941 - 1 July 1977) was a German ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1968 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:1977 deaths Category:German male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of East Germany Category:Ski jumpers at the 1968 Winter Olympics Category:People from Johanngeorgenstadt
